## ğŸ“ Task: Add Color and Font with CSS

ğŸ‘‰ **Your mission:** Link a CSS file and add a few basic styles.

1. **Create and link your CSS file**
   - In your folder `web/level2/`, create a new file called `style.css`.
   - Open your `index.html` and inside the `<head>` section add:
     ```html
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
     ```
   > ğŸ§  *Definition:* `<link rel="stylesheet">` tells your page to use your style rules from another file.

2. **Set a background color**
   In `style.css`, type:
   ```css
   body {
     background-color: lightblue;
   }

	3.	Change your text color and font

